      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "EZRA KAI (6) hasn't raced since the Vicbred Super Series 3CG Final here last November but has been readied for the return with two nice trials. Draws wide but finds a winnable assignment first up. DOSSIER (1) was well in the market last start but copped a check and broke. Was also let down by manners two back so she'll need to get this right but has winning claims from the ace draw if she produces her best. DELS DESTINY NZ (3) has produced some decent efforts since a Ballarat win last month including a placing in this grade two back at Kilmore. Draws for a good showing. There was merit in the latest performance of THE SKY IS THE LIMIT (4) when she came from the back line for fourth at this venue.",
